### OpenAPI Token 获取测试
### 测试客户端凭证授权流程

### 1. 正常的token获取请求
POST http://localhost:9010/v1/oauth2/token
Authorization: Basic SDEyZV9ZUlBuTEZMSE1ZcTpJUFNHLVliRERKNENfdHNjRC1PdVlmcmZTbVZXOFVLVg==
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials

###
POST http://localhost:9000/v1/oauth2/introspect
Authorization: Basic SDEyZV9ZUlBuTEZMSE1ZcTpJUFNHLVliRERKNENfdHNjRC1PdVlmcmZTbVZXOFVLVg==
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

token=_KgzJs-fmEbW7G-whcQ7PuFzXl-Zvt8J

### 2. 测试无效的grant_type
POST http://localhost:9000/v2/oauth2/token
Authorization: Basic Y2wwMGI4MTU3MWQ4OTE2ZDI6MTZkYzU5ODUzNTgxZmNlNWI5MjFkMmU4OGRlN2RjYjU2ZTRiMzA1YQ==
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=authorization_code

### 3. 测试缺少Authorization头
POST http://localhost:9000/v2/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials

### 4. 测试无效的Basic认证格式
POST http://localhost:9000/v2/oauth2/token
Authorization: Basic invalid_base64
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials

### 5. 测试不存在的appId
POST http://localhost:9000/v2/oauth2/token
Authorization: Basic bm90X2V4aXN0OnNlY3JldA==
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials

### 注意：
### - 示例中的Base64编码 Y2wwMGI4MTU3MWQ4OTE2ZDI6MTZkYzU5ODUzNTgxZmNlNWI5MjFkMmU4OGRlN2RjYjU2ZTRiMzA1YQ== 
###   解码后为: cl00b81571d8916d2:16dc59853581fce5b921d2e88de7dcb56e4b305a
### - 需要确保数据库中存在对应的appId和appSecret
### - 返回格式应该为: {"access_token": "xxx", "expires_in": 7200}